KNOWN BUGS:
 HIGH PRIORITY:
  [ ] Get rid of Text::selections_mut.
  [ ] Modification of Text in BufferUpdated hook should be disallowed.
  [ ] Indentation is inefficient.
  [ ] Some strange slowdowns on Buffer switching and reindentation.
 LOW PRIORITY:
  [ ] Selections struct that holds a reference to the Bytes.
    [ ] Also make the Bytes-less version inaccessible.
  [ ] statics remain as the program reloads.
  [ ] Perfect print iterators.
    [ ] Perfect words iterator.
  [ ] tree-sitter-duat-text is not being used.
  [ ] For now, on Windows, duat can only reload if there is only one instance open.
  [ ] Locking a Mutex on every Change is surely slow.

